com.esri.mo2.data.omc
Interface Cacheable

public interface Cacheable

This interface implements a Selectable Dataset that can be registered with com.esri.mo2.data.omc.Cache. When the Cache decides to get more data from the Dataset, it invokes Cacheable's retrieve method.

Method Summary
 Cursor retrieve(SelectionSet sset)
          This method is invoked by the associated Cache in a separate Thread, when it wants to obtain more data.
 

Method Detail

retrieve

public Cursor retrieve(SelectionSet sset)
This method is invoked by the associated Cache in a separate Thread, when it wants to obtain more data. This method fetches the required data from the external data source.

Parameters:
sset - identifies the objects required to be retrieved
Returns:
a cursor
